{
  "title": "ISic003599. Inscription recording construction by Cresconius",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/RHXWRC83\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/RHXWRC83</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>In nomine D(omi)ni n(ostri) <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ihesu\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ihesu\"><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ih</span>(es)<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">u</span></span></span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Cresconius\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Cresconius\">Cresconius</span></span> s(anctum) <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>opus <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"☧risti\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"☧risti\">☧(rist)i</span></span> edificabit </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/RHXWRC83\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/RHXWRC83</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>INNOMINEDNIN<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ihesu\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ihesu\"><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">IH</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">U</span></span></span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Cresconius\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Cresconius\">CRESCONIUS</span></span>S<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>OPUS<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"☧risti\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"☧risti\">☧I</span></span>EDIFICABIT</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text after Rizzone and Sammito 2004</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>In the name of our lord Jesus, Cresconius built the sacred work of Christ</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>Nel nome del Signore nostro Gesù, Crosconius la santa opera di Cristo edificò</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 2007.0677 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283</a></li><li> Rizzone Sammito 2004 104-105 fig.2 </li><li> Sammito and Rizzone 2007 1623-1624 tav.9.6 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001606\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001606</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Simple latin letters, use of supraline</p> Line 1-3  50-80  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
